Natasha Little https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natasha_Little 0 Natasha Little (born 2 October 1969) is an English actress. She is best known for her roles in Another Life as Edith Thompson, in the BBC show The Night Manager as Lady Caroline Langbourne, and in the show Thirteen as Christina Moxam.
